# NestJS Modules â€” Structural Rules

- Every module must contain:
  - `Controller`
  - `Service`
  - `DTOs`
  - (Optional) `Repository`
- Each module must export its own providers
- Avoid cross-module imports between unrelated features
- Each module must log using `LoggerService` with proper context (`moduleName`)
- Standard layout:
```

src/modules/tasks/
tasks.module.ts
tasks.controller.ts
tasks.service.ts
dto/

```
